terprises transitioning to password-less authentication and never worry about a data breach again.Become HYPR_Secure Select Any Biometrics Instantly add voice, face, touch, eye, palm or any combination of authenticators for a secure digital experience. Secure Your Applications Unlock the power of our next-gen biometric multi-factor authentication in any application, on any device. Deploy to Millions of Users With the push of a button, deploy HYPR’s omni-channel authentication to all of your customers, employees, and partners.                      



